net.sourceforge.jaad.mp4.api

Class MetaData

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.sourceforge.jaad.mp4.api.MetaData

  • public class MetaData
extends java.lang.Object
    This class contains the metadata for a movie. It parses different metadata types (iTunes tags, ID3). The fields can be read via the get(Field) method using one of the predefined Fields.
